    "result": {"data":{"allWebmention":{"totalCount":0,"edges":[]},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Text modules are familiar from word processing programmes. Text passages that are often repeated can be added with a click. You can proceed in a similar way with formats in TinyMCE. I am interested in the general principle. That is why the example here is again kept simple. A text is simply given a red background.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Cassiopeia offers Bootstrap 5. Get inspired for your own use cases in the <a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/getting-started/introduction/\">Bootstrap Documentation</a>[getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0], if you don't already have a lot of ideas yourself. An often used use case is a table that is created for design purposes only. In HTML, it is a bad idea to use a table for presentation purposes only, because it does not reflect the semantics. Other elements make more semantic sense and look just like a table. In the simplest case, the <a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/layout/grid/\">Grid</a>[^getbootstrap.com/docs/5.0/layout/grid/]<!-- \\index{Tiny!Tempalte erstellen} --><!-- \\index{Editor Tiny MCE!Tempalte erstellen} --></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"create-a-template-for-use-in-tinymce-in-joomla-4\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#create-a-template-for-use-in-tinymce-in-joomla-4\" aria-label=\"create a template for use in tinymce in joomla 4 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Create a template for use in TinyMCE in Joomla 4.</h2>\n<p>First we create the file <code class=\"language-text\">redBackground.html</code> in the directory <code class=\"language-text\">/templates/cassiopeia/html/tinymce/</code>.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk3\">&lt;!-- /templates/cassiopeia/html/tinymce/redBackground.html --&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&quot;redbackground&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk4\">p</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">Text</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">p</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk4\">div</span><span class=\"mtk17\">&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>You must adapt the paths shown in the following image to your individual environment if you are not using Cassiopeia as the standard template - or a child template.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/d698c/tiny1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.99999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        title=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        src=\"/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/5a190/tiny1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/772e8/tiny1.png 200w,\n/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/e17e5/tiny1.png 400w,\n/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/5a190/tiny1.png 800w,\n/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/c1b63/tiny1.png 1200w,\n/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/29007/tiny1.png 1600w,\n/static/81ae97e4b2dc1a5eea2b9896c1cc57da/d698c/tiny1.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Now create an article and select the menu item for inserting a template in the TinyMCE menu.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/d698c/tiny2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        title=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        src=\"/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/5a190/tiny2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/772e8/tiny2.png 200w,\n/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/e17e5/tiny2.png 400w,\n/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/5a190/tiny2.png 800w,\n/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/c1b63/tiny2.png 1200w,\n/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/29007/tiny2.png 1600w,\n/static/2a9e7c5d5428cfbebd223b03f1625c6e/d698c/tiny2.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>If there are several templates in your installation, you can choose.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/d698c/tiny3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        title=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        src=\"/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/5a190/tiny3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/772e8/tiny3.png 200w,\n/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/e17e5/tiny3.png 400w,\n/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/5a190/tiny3.png 800w,\n/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/c1b63/tiny3.png 1200w,\n/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/29007/tiny3.png 1600w,\n/static/41921dbc9b8f1a8abfacbc3d58d6e6bc/d698c/tiny3.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Depending on which HTML markup your template contains, it is now inserted. If you have used my simple example, the code <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div class=\"redbackground\">&lt;p>Text&lt;/p>&lt;/div></code> will be inserted.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/d698c/tiny4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        title=\"Joomla Tiny MCE Template erstellen - Einstellungen\"\n        src=\"/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/5a190/tiny4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/772e8/tiny4.png 200w,\n/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/e17e5/tiny4.png 400w,\n/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/5a190/tiny4.png 800w,\n/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/c1b63/tiny4.png 1200w,\n/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/29007/tiny4.png 1600w,\n/static/4c8207b31cc5068a896b02309ec32e43/d698c/tiny4.png 1846w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: ' ';\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-add::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-add-background-color, rgba(0, 255, 60, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-diff-del::before {\n    background-color: var(--grvsc-line-diff-del-background-color, rgba(255, 0, 20, 0.2));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line-number {\n    padding: 0 2p